[normal]I am currently the chair of the Wiltshire Police Branch of the Police Federation of England and 
[normal]Wales
[normal].  My previous recent roles within Wiltshire Police provide me with background experience which may provide alternative perspectives which ma
[normal]y be of use to the enquiry.  The role I currently undertake also helps me combine my strategic knowledge with that of the views and experiences of frontline officers.
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]1.2
[normal]&#xa0; 
[normal]Prior to joining Wiltshire Police
[normal] 
[normal]I gained a degree in Mathematics, Statistics and Compu
[normal]ting.  I have now been a police officer for over twenty five years.  The majority of this time has been spent in uniform working within the local policing environment.   
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]1.3
[normal]&#xa0; 
[normal]In 2005 I
[normal] became an Inspector in the force control room.  As such I have significant
[normal] operational experience of the recording of reported incidents and the initial investigation of such reports.
[normal]  In early 2009 
[normal]I 
[normal]moved into the force performance team.  During my time in the performance team I had significant involvement in:
[normal]i.
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]Professionalisin
[normal]g the work of the team to focus on more insightful analysis of force data to drive performance improvement.
[normal]ii.
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
