[normal]iQuanta
[normal] 
[normal]data to drive performance.
[normal] (Paragraph 4)
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]2.3
[normal]&#xa0; 
[normal]HMIC seeking evidence only on the under recording of crime not the accurate recording of crime.
[normal] (Paragraph 
[normal]5
[normal])
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]2.4
[normal]&#xa0; 
[normal]Evidence of over recording of crimes 
[normal]in cases of common assault. 
[normal](Paragraph 
[normal]6
[normal])
[normal]&#xa0;
